<html>
<head>
    <title>TIY Java Gradle Template</title>
</head>
<body>
<h2>Requirements for the Java Back-end assignments Aug 2016:</h2>

<blockquote>
    There are 33 total assignments. These 9 are out of scope for grading, though you'll still need to turn in an attempt.
    <br/>
    That leaves 24 assignments that need to be 85% completed (20).
</blockquote>
<ol id="assignments">
<table border="0" cellspacing="5">
    <th>Name</th>
    <th>Description</th>
    <th>Required?</th>
    {{#assignments}}
    <tr>
        <td><li>{{name}}</li></td>
        <td>{{description}}</td>
        <td>[ {{required}} ]<span style="visibility: hidden;">{{id}}</span> </td>
    </tr>
    {{/assignments}}
</table>
</ol>

<script>
    function inactivate() {
        var tr = document.getElementById("assignments");
        var items = tr.getElementsByTagName("tr");
        var cells;
        for (var i = 0; i < items.length; ++i) {
            if (items[i].innerHTML.indexOf('true') < 0 && i > 0 ) {
                cells = items[i].getElementsByTagName('td');
                cells[2].style.backgroundColor = 'pink';
            }
        }
    }
    inactivate();
</script>

</body>
</html>